Recently went down to LA to play the @jumpstartdesigners fundraiser to help underprivileged youth get the tools they need to be creative. Thanks to @em0n33y and @my_cousin_vinny for making it happen and all the friends that came to hang. We’ll be back real real soon.

#la #losangles #discoverla

Remember Risqué? Well in collaboration with @this916 and @lowbrau916 this Thursday 12/22 we’re going to relive some of our favorite nights with music from that time in a series of parties featuring some of our favorites artists and djs in that era of music. First up is one of the bloghouse era’s favorite dj and producer’s, @tittsworth. He’s one of the owners of Crybaby(@crybabyoakland), a new venue in Oakland, his label Hermanito(@hermanitolabel) with Dave Nada of Nadastrom, and the legendary U Street Music Hall. As a dj and producer, he’s put out timeless releases and worked with an array of artists. Myself and @holywater.jaked.jacknife will be the other djs for the evening. Follow @fortheluvofblog, @this916, and @lowbrau916 for updates and grab presale entry.

#916 #sacramento #sactown #bloghouse

I called my friends at @lowbrau916 and @this916 with an idea for a special Paradise Dayclub now here we are.

First big one of the year with @pangeasound crew @djsupernova @joaqu.n @falcons @joe_vs_joe who’ve been dominating the worldly sounds and hosting parties all over the country, and most recently Boiler Room. Myself and @my_cousin_vinny on opening duties! Save the date and get your tickets asap.

#sacramento #916 #afrobeats #housemusic

🚨 In collaboration with @lowbrau916 and @this916 we are bringing bloghouse legend @uffieufficial to @fortheluvofblog Sacramento Thu. 1/26! She was a major player in the in the bloghouse scene on @edbanger with her hits like “Pop The Glock”, “ADD SUV ft. Pharrell” and is still making waves with her new album “Sunshine Factory” on Toro Y Moi’s label @company.records and recent collaboration with The Blessed Madonna. 

Myself and and @holywater.jaked.jacknife will be playing all the bloghouse hits you remember or never heard. Presale tickets are available now!

#sacramento #916 #sactown #bloghouse #uffie

Sunday is almost here and that means @pangeasound makes their Sacramento debut at @lowbrau916! Tickets still available now. Head to @this916 for the link and see you Sunday!

We started @fortheluvofblog to shine light on artists and music that played a major influence in a special time and still now. High on that list is @uffieufficial and she’ll be joining us for the second installment of this party. Resident dj’s @holywater.jaked.syndicate and myself will be playing bloghouse hits you loved and maybe missed.

Tickets are still available just follow the link in the For the Love of Blog bio. See you tomorrow Thur. 1/26 9pm at @lowbrau916.
